title: Championship Manager 97/98 (cm9798) and utilities
description:
Championship Manager 2 97/98, version 2.93-- reloaded with even more extras!


This contains the classic football / soccer management game, plus a lot of extra utilities and editors:

cmagent.exe           Flagship CME Agent 1.1
cmfind.exe            CM Find
cmtimetravel.exe      CM Time Travel (teleport yourself through the preseason, etc.)
cmwiz.exe             CM Wiz (for 8mb or 16mb v2.93 games)
cmx16.exe             Mind Compression&#039;s Explorer (16mb game in v2.93)
cmx8.exe              Mind Compression&#039;s Explorer (8 mb game)
scout16.exe           Mind Compression&#039;s Scout (16mb)
scout8.exe            Mind Compression&#039;s Scout (8 mb)
trainmg.exe           Manager Trainer (16mb games in v2.93 only)
